nodes.text: The year 3632 BBY was a period of galactic history. That year, the anarchist Kaliyo Djannis arrived on Zakuul and began a campaign of bombings in the Spire. Leontyne Saresh's terms limits as Supreme Chancellor of the Galactic Republic ran out in that year, and she was succeeded by Jebevel Madon.
